Disseram que verificariam.

365
00:32:33,637 --> 00:32:35,086
Inúteis!

366
00:32:36,709 --> 00:32:38,403
Merda! Merda!

367
00:32:38,404 --> 00:32:40,265
<i>Sabia que mesmo
a 160km de distância,</i>

368
00:32:40,266 --> 00:32:41,875
